      <title>泰晤士水务公司竞标者 Covalis 将与 Octopus Energy 部门合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/thames-water-bidder-covalis-to-partner-with-octopus-energy-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果股权融资成功，Covalis Capital 将与 Octopus Energy Group 的技术部门 Kraken 合作，帮助泰晤士水务公司管理其 1600 万客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/thames-water-bidder-covalis-to-partner-with-octopus-energy-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 13:59:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sardine 融资 7000 万美元，用于打造反欺诈 AI 代理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/sardine-raises-70-million-to-build-fraud-fighting-ai-agents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sardine 是一个为企业客户解决欺诈、合规和信用承保的风险平台，该公司表示已筹集 7000 万美元的股权资金，这笔资金将用于帮助扩大该初创公司针对自动合规和风险流程的人工智能代理套件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/sardine-raises-70-million-to-build-fraud-fighting-ai-agents</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
